attributes.Long form description: The student attaches the Joy-Con controllers to the handheld, then detaches them and attaches them to the Nintendo Switch, after that the detaches the Joy-Con controllers and inserts them into the Joy-Con strap, making sure they are locked. The student stands the Nintendo Switch on the table with the kickstand, then he exchanges the game card and the SD Card, and finally he turns on and off the Nintendo switch.
